a1f8ba26-447e-4245-a8d1-1f4dfa3bead0.instructions:
Have you purchased and receiving a Final Fantasy XIV Time Card from us per email? If so, you can now exchange your code and start exploring the online world of Final Fantasy. Redeeming your FFXIV Time Card can be done like this: Log in to your FINAL FANTASY XIV: Mog Station account;
Click on “Account Services” in the top left corner of your screen;
After that, click on “Renew Subscription (Game Card)”;
Enter the code you received per email and follow the instructions on your screen to complete the activation.

